6841432.name: Tangy Chole Quesadilla
6841432.description: Tangy chole wrapped in crispy laccha paratha and baked with veggies and chipotle infused cheese.

6841433.name: Bombay Masala Quesadilla
6841433.description: Oh Bombay, you are incomplete without that smack of a masala potato grilled toast sandwich! Paying homage to this incredible city is our Bombay masala quesadilla that adds in the same mellow, spicy flavours but with a twist: find a layer of gooey chipotle infused cheese to bind the flavours in.

6841434.name: Smokey Beans Quesadilla
6841434.description: The nutty flavours from beans and smoked gravies gives our smokey bean quesadilla a distinct flavour- one that is worthy of connoisseurs. While you are at it, appreciate the subtle flavours and the varied textures that play each other off.

6841435.name: Chicken Keema Quesadilla
6841435.description: Another favourite is baida roti which is essentially chicken paratha and we couldnt resist a good quesadilla with the same flavours! Chicken keema stuffed laccha paratha, baked with veggies and chipotle cheese is outright heaven.

6841436.name: Pimento & Sausages Quesadilla
6841436.description: Red bell pepper and chicken sausage is a winner and we have roped in the flavours in our pimento and sausage quesadilla. To add in a dash of heat, we add chipotle cheese.

6841437.name: Masala Chicken Quesadilla
6841437.description: Taking cues from the big, beautiful flavours of bhuna chicken and masala chicken quesadilla packs in oodles of flavours along with veggies and chipotle cheese in a crispy laccha paratha.

6841439.name: Chipotle Meatball Quesadilla
6841439.description: Now who does not love chicken meatballs and more so if its wrapped in a healthy, hearty and crispy quesadilla with creamy chipotle cheese.

6841440.name: Four Beans Lasagne
6841440.description: Four kind of Indian beans cooked to a smokey, creamy consistency and layered with lasagne sheets. Baked to a light golden brown!

6841441.name: Chicken Keema Lasagne
6841441.description: An Italian favourite with a heart of India. Our chicken keema lasagne upholds big Indian flavours in this Italian layered delicacy.

6841442.name: Roasted Chicken Steak
6841442.description: Fresh flavours, borrowed from Sunday roast herbs like rosemary and thyme, in our chicken steak with flavoured rice, BBQ sauce and freshly picked salad.

6841443.name: Achari Fish Steak
6841443.description: Marinade soaked basa fillets grilled in a hot oven and served with rice pilaf, BBQ sauce and fresh salad.

6841447.name: Tandoori Kukkad Pot Rice
6841447.description: Tandoori kukkad is a north Indian chicken specialty and our pot rice embraces the quintessential flavours quite right. We add in a little surprise with browned butter in this delish and cheesy one pot meal.
